                                                        <li>
                        <div class="pe_left">
                            <a href="http://www.cio.com.cn/space/index/6" class="p1"><img src="http://www.cio.com.cn/avatar/small/6" /></a>
                            <a href="http://www.cio.com.cn/space/index/6" class="name">徐蕊</a>
